Revision history for WebService-Libris

0.08    2014-01-03
        Update to non-ancient Mojolicious

0.07    2012-03-09
        Remove deprecated use of Mojo::DOM->new() with arguments
        Fixes failure reports by recent CPAN smokers

0.06
        Switch to Module::Build

0.05    2011-06-28
        Add missing FileCache.pm
        more elaborate language handling
        remove nonsensical -T from test shebang lines

0.03    2011-06-28
        Documentation for all interesting classes
        More accessors
        Caching
        Unit tests
        Got rid of WebService::Libris::Collection

0.02    2011-06-19
        Improved documentation
        Accessors are a bit more robust

0.01    2011-06-18
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
